00:10:27,260 --> 00:10:29,194


175
00:10:33,967 --> 00:10:36,401
我们到了！
We're here!

176
00:10:36,403 --> 00:10:38,169
安柏，快醒醒。
Amber, wake up.

177
00:10:38,171 --> 00:10:40,271
干嘛呀？我们到哪儿了？
What's going on? Where are we?

178
00:10:40,273 --> 00:10:42,907
我们到阿瓦洛了。
We're in Avalor.

179
00:10:42,909 --> 00:10:45,610
收起船帆！
Ease the mainsail!

180
00:10:45,612 --> 00:10:48,413


181
00:10:50,250 --> 00:10:51,850
立正！
Attention!

182
00:10:59,960 --> 00:11:02,327
很壮观，不是吗？
Quite a sight, is it not?

183
00:11:02,329 --> 00:11:04,996
阿瓦洛王国。
The kingdom of Avalor.

184
00:11:06,099 --> 00:11:07,999
在这么大的城市里我要怎么找到
How am I going to find Alacazar's house

185
00:11:08,001 --> 00:11:10,769
阿拉卡扎的家啊？！
in that huge city?

186
00:11:10,771 --> 00:11:12,103
早上好，巴期克斯将军。
Good morning, Admiral Vazquez.

187
00:11:12,105 --> 00:11:13,838
国王陛下。
Your Majesty.

188
00:11:13,840 --> 00:11:16,841
你能代我们向史瑞奇女王问好吗？
Have you sent word of our arrival to Queen Shuriki?

189
00:11:16,843 --> 00:11:19,277
- 一小时前我已经派人去了。 - 很好。
- We sent a launch an hour ago. - Excellent.

190
00:11:19,279 --> 00:11:20,979
你为什么要那样做？
Why did you do that?

191
00:11:20,981 --> 00:11:22,947
向国王或女王问好是皇室成员
It's the royal custom to greet the king or queen

192
00:11:22,949 --> 00:11:25,050
来访新王国时的惯例，苏菲亚。
when visiting a new kingdom, Sofia.

193
00:11:25,052 --> 00:11:26,518
我们要去见她吗？
We have to meet her?

194
00:11:26,520 --> 00:11:28,353
当然，这不是很好吗？
Yes. Isn't it exciting?

195
00:11:45,872 --> 00:11:48,139
史瑞奇女王！
Queen Shuriki!

196
00:11:48,141 --> 00:11:50,975
哦！别再那样子悄悄靠近我，埃斯特班。
Oh! Don't sneak up on me like that, Esteban.

197
00:11:50,977 --> 00:11:53,311
你没看到我在为接见客人
Can't you see I'm putting on my best face

198
00:11:53,313 --> 00:11:55,547
做准备吗？
for our visitors?

199
00:11:55,549 --> 00:11:58,216
哦，我要等你准备好了再找你吗？
Oh, should I come back when you are finished?

200
00:11:58,218 --> 00:12:00,585
我已经准备好了。
I am finished.

201
00:12:00,587 --> 00:12:03,354
是的是的，女王陛下，我的疏忽。
Of course you are, my queen. My mistake.

202
00:12:03,356 --> 00:12:06,958
是时候迎接罗伦国王了。
It is time to greet King Roland of Enchancia.

203
00:12:09,162 --> 00:12:12,363
任何事情都得做到最好，阿芒多。
Everything must look its absolute best, Armando.

204
00:12:12,365 --> 00:12:13,998
是的，女王陛下。
Yes, Your Grace.

205
00:12:14,000 --> 00:12:16,701
我花了许多年时间来改造这里，
I have spent years making this the cleanest, quietest,

206
00:12:16,703 --> 00:12:19,070
使它成为世上最有秩序的国家。
most orderly kingdom in the world.

207
00:12:19,072 --> 00:12:21,005
任何事情都做得非常到位，
Nothing is out of place,

208
00:12:21,007 --> 00:12:22,273
每个人都在做他们该做的，
everyone does what they're told,

209
00:12:22,275 --> 00:12:24,409
不会抗命。
no unruliness.

210
00:12:26,113 --> 00:12:31,116
没有讨厌的叮叮当当的铃声或者音乐，
No irritating jingle-jangle of bells or music.

211
00:12:31,118 --> 00:12:33,251
只有简单的和平与宁静。
Just simple peace and quiet.

212
00:12:33,253 --> 00:12:34,919
也没人会偷看我洗澡，女王陛下。
No one will make a peep, Your Grace.

213
00:12:34,921 --> 00:12:38,056
当然除了我那些臣民们的欢呼声。
Except the cheers of my subjects, of course.

214
00:12:38,058 --> 00:12:41,359
看来那些人又要欢呼一次了，
And the cheering crowds will be cheering this time,

215
00:12:41,361 --> 00:12:43,695
说得对吧，埃斯特班？
correct, Esteban?

216
00:12:43,697 --> 00:12:48,566
我们派了皇家卫队来镇压秩序。
We sent the royal guards ahead to offer encouragement.

217
00:12:48,568 --> 00:12:50,034
很好！
Perfect.

218
00:12:51,972 --> 00:12:54,906


219
00:12:54,908 --> 00:12:56,975
你们好！你们好！
Hello. Hello.

220
00:13:01,715 --> 00:13:03,581
看来我们很受欢迎！
This is quite a welcome.

221
00:13:03,583 --> 00:13:05,416
我想说...
I'll say.

222
00:13:05,418 --> 00:13:07,752
你们好，你们好！
Hello. Hello!

223
00:13:07,754 --> 00:13:09,454
他们很喜欢我。
They really like me.

224
00:13:12,993 --> 00:13:17,162
但他们更喜欢她。
they like her even more.

225
00:13:17,164 --> 00:13:19,063
我得和她保持距离，安柏。
I'd keep my distance, Amber.

226
00:13:19,065 --> 00:13:22,233
是的，你们爱戴的女王来了。
Yes, your beloved queen has arrived.

227
00:13:22,235 --> 00:13:24,235
再欢呼一下吧！
Cheer like you mean it.

228
00:13:24,237 --> 00:13:26,638
欢迎来到阿瓦洛！
Welcome to Avalor.

229
00:13:26,640 --> 00:13:29,174
我是史瑞奇女王。
I am Queen Shuriki.

230
00:13:29,176 --> 00:13:32,010
我是埃斯特班大臣。
And I am Chancellor Esteban.

231
00:13:32,012 --> 00:13:34,179
你们能来我的的王国度假
It is an honor that you have chosen to visit

232
00:13:34,181 --> 00:13:36,347
是我们的荣幸！
our humble kingdom.

233
00:13:36,349 --> 00:13:39,818
很荣幸你们能如此热情的接待我们，史瑞奇女王。
You honor us with such a warm reception, Queen Shuriki.

234
00:13:39,820 --> 00:13:41,452
那是阿瓦洛的习俗，罗伦国王。
That is the Avaloran way, King Roland.

235
00:13:41,454 --> 00:13:43,188


236
00:13:43,190 --> 00:13:45,390
哦，多么美妙的音乐！
Oh, what pretty music.

237
00:13:49,029 --> 00:13:52,597
现在让我们去皇宫。
Now let us adjourn to the palace.

238
00:13:52,599 --> 00:13:54,232
埃斯特班，那个长笛。
Esteban, the flute.

239
00:14:01,441 --> 00:14:03,174
嘿！
Hey!

240
00:14:05,045 --> 00:14:07,178


241
00:14:07,180 --> 00:14:09,347
上去吧，公主。
After you, princess.

242
00:15:09,042 --> 00:15:11,509
这座宫殿是在数百年前建成的，
The palace was built centuries ago.

243
00:15:11,511 --> 00:15:14,012
我还有点事情要处理，如果你们要找我，
It's a little busy, if you ask me.

244
00:15:14,014 --> 00:15:16,915
这里是我的大殿。
And this is my throne room.

245
00:15:16,917 --> 00:15:19,250
我大部分时间都在这里。
I spend most of my time here.

246
00:15:19,252 --> 00:15:21,252
看起来怎么样？
So what do you think?

247
00:15:21,254 --> 00:15:23,121
那王座可真漂亮。
That's quite a throne.

248
00:15:23,123 --> 00:15:25,123
谢谢！
Thank you.

249
00:15:25,125 --> 00:15:27,692
为了建造这个我派人花了十年时间来挖钻石，
Took them over a decade to dig up all the diamonds.

250
00:15:27,694 --> 00:15:30,395
但这值得等待。
But it was worth the wait.

251
00:15:30,397 --> 00:15:32,096
别碰那个！
Don't touch that!

252
00:15:32,098 --> 00:15:34,198
詹姆士，你的礼貌哪儿去了？
James, where are your manners?

253
00:15:34,200 --> 00:15:37,101
这是一个非常脆弱的织制画像。
It's a very delicate fabric.

254
00:15:37,103 --> 00:15:39,103
快过来，孩子。
Come along, my boy.

255
00:15:39,105 --> 00:15:42,240
你们航行了这么长的时间一定饿了吧，
You must all be famished after such a long journey,

256
00:15:42,242 --> 00:15:45,376
所以我...我是说，女王特意让厨师准备了
so I... I mean, the queen, had the chefs prepare

257
00:15:45,378 --> 00:15:47,979
一些地道的美食。
a small taste of the local cuisine.

258
00:15:49,783 --> 00:15:51,549
哦，这一路上的景色可真美啊
Oh, it's such a lovely view

259
00:15:51,551 --> 00:15:53,284
史瑞奇女王！
from up here, Queen Shuriki.

260
00:15:53,286 --> 00:15:55,887
我已经迫不及待想去城市里看看
I can't wait to go back down to the city

261
00:15:55,889 --> 00:15:57,755
那些漂亮的老房子
and look at all the beautiful old houses.

262
00:15:57,757 --> 00:15:59,123
老房子？
Old houses?

263
00:15:59,125 --> 00:16:02,093
那就是你最想看的东西吗？亲爱的？
That's the last thing you should be looking at, dear.

264
00:16:02,095 --> 00:16:04,262
我们的商场和公园绝对才是
Our marketplace and park lands

265
00:16:04,264 --> 00:16:06,230
不二的选择。
are second to none.

266
00:16:06,232 --> 00:16:07,632
埃斯特班，取消我的工作计划，
Esteban, clear my schedule.

267
00:16:07,634 --> 00:16:09,434
我下午要亲自陪我们的客人
I shall personally give our guests

268
00:16:09,436 --> 00:16:11,336
去城市里逛逛！
a tour of the city this afternoon.

269
00:16:11,338 --> 00:16:14,339
嘿嘿！午餐吃什么？史瑞奇？
Hey, hey, what's for lunch, Shuriki?

270
00:16:14,341 --> 00:16:15,440
那些是什么？
What are those?

271
00:16:15,442 --> 00:16:17,275
噢，那是飞豹，
Oh, those are jaquins.

272
00:16:17,277 --> 00:16:19,177
传说中的魔法生物，
Magical creatures of legend.

273
00:16:19,179 --> 00:16:20,979
阿瓦洛的象征！
Majestic symbols of Avalor.

274
00:16:20,981 --> 00:16:23,181
它们曾经被画在国旗上，
They used to be symbols of our kingdom.

275
00:16:23,183 --> 00:16:25,350
但现在却只会令人生厌。
Now they are just a nuisance.

276
00:16:25,352 --> 00:16:26,751
为什么？
Why is that?

277
00:16:26,753 --> 00:16:29,787
因为我们会唱歌！哈哈！
Because we sing. Ha ha!

278
00:16:29,789 --> 00:16:32,423
从迷雾丛林到高地
? From the misty jungle highlands ?

279
00:16:32,425 --> 00:16:34,292
我们的翅膀永不停
? We fan our wings and fly ?

280
00:16:34,294 --> 00:16:36,427
我们会逗人们笑
? To delight all Avalorans ?

281
00:16:36,429 --> 00:16:38,863
我们也会惹人哭
? With our mighty jaquin cry ?

282
00:16:38,865 --> 00:16:41,265
它们在唱歌！
They're singing!

283
00:16:41,267 --> 00:16:43,101
你能相信吗，苏菲亚？
Can you believe that, Sofia?

284
00:16:43,103 --> 00:16:44,335
会说话的动物！
Talking animals!

285
00:16:44,337 --> 00:16:45,837
有谁以前见过或者听说过这种事吗？
Who ever heard of such a thing?

286
00:16:45,839 --> 00:16:48,973
好东西要分享，朋友！
Let's dig in, amigos!

287
00:16:48,975 --> 00:16:51,776
噢呵呵！看起来很好吃！
Oh, ho, ho, that looks tasty.

288
00:16:51,778 --> 00:16:54,178
嘿！小心点，斯凯勒！
Hey, save room for dessert, Skylar.

289
00:16:54,180 --> 00:16:56,180
不管是谁叫你们在外面吃饭
My compliments to the chef

290
00:16:56,182 --> 00:16:58,216
都代我向厨师致谢！
and whoever said you should eat outside,

291
00:16:58,218 --> 00:16:59,817
因为这想法太赞啦！
'cause that is a great idea!

292
00:16:59,819 --> 00:17:01,352
绝对赞！
Brilliant.

293
00:17:01,354 --> 00:17:04,022
噢。。咻咻！快走开，看你们干的好事！
Oh, shoo. Get out of here, you pests.

294
00:17:04,024 --> 00:17:06,057
啊？可我们才刚来啊！
Aw, but we just got here.

295
00:17:06,059 --> 00:17:08,292
你可以命令别人该做些什么，
You can tell the people what to do,

296
00:17:08,294 --> 00:17:09,527
但你不能命令我们！
but you can't boss us around.

297
00:17:09,529 --> 00:17:11,195
你能拿我们怎么样？你又抓不到我们！
Mess with a jaquin, you get the claws.

298
00:17:11,197 --> 00:17:13,731
你们闹够了没有，我已经忍无可忍了！
That's it. Enough is enough.

299
00:17:13,733 --> 00:17:16,734
让我们进去吃，好吗？
Let's finish our meal inside, shall we?

300
00:17:17,704 --> 00:17:19,670
好！好！好！
Yes, yes.

301
00:17:19,672 --> 00:17:21,572
我们都进去吧！
Let's all go inside.

302
00:17:28,314 --> 00:17:31,482


303
00:17:33,486 --> 00:17:36,921
嗯，从史瑞奇那里拿来的食物味道真不错。
Mmm. Food tastes better when we take it from Shuriki.

304
00:17:36,923 --> 00:17:39,223
把爪子舔干净。
It's paw-licking good.

305
00:17:39,225 --> 00:17:41,225
芒果的味道真不错！
This mango is sublime.

306
00:17:41,227 --> 00:17:43,361
呃，打扰一下！
Um, excuse me.

307
00:17:43,363 --> 00:17:45,930
嘿，你还在外面做什么？
Hey, what are you still doing out here?

308
00:17:45,932 --> 00:17:48,866
我不确定，但我想求你们帮我一个忙。
I'm not exactly sure, but maybe you can help me.

309
00:17:48,868 --> 00:17:51,269
我们决不会帮史瑞奇的朋友。
We do not help friends of Shuriki.

310
00:17:51,271 --> 00:17:53,104
我不是她的朋友。
I'm not her friend.

311
00:17:53,106 --> 00:17:54,672
我的家人只是来这里度假。
My family had to visit the palace.

312
00:17:54,674 --> 00:17:56,908
我真的很急着要找到阿拉卡扎的家。
I really came here to find Alacazar's house.

313
00:17:56,910 --> 00:17:58,543
阿拉卡扎是谁？
Who's Alacazar?

314
00:17:58,545 --> 00:18:01,412
很久以前的那个皇家巫师，记得吗？
He was the old royal wizard. Remember?

315
00:18:01,414 --> 00:18:03,848
哦，想起来了！
Oh, yeah.

316
00:18:03,850 --> 00:18:05,516
他不是在史瑞奇入侵之后就失踪了吗？
Didn't he split after Shuriki took over?

317
00:18:05,518 --> 00:18:07,251
这能怪他吗？
Who can blame him?

318
00:18:07,253 --> 00:18:08,886
她可能已经把他杀了，
She probably would've zapped him

319
00:18:08,888 --> 00:18:11,456
就像国王和皇后一样，还有艾莲娜公主！
like the king and queen, and Princess Elena.

320
00:18:11,458 --> 00:18:14,559
- 那么年轻！ - 那么勇敢！ - 可怜的艾莲娜！
- So young. - So brave. - Poor Elena.

321
00:18:14,561 --> 00:18:17,095
好吧，如果我告诉你们我有办法能
Well, what if I told you I know a way

322
00:18:17,097 --> 00:18:19,030
救回艾莲娜公主呢？
to bring Princess Elena back?

323
00:18:19,032 --> 00:18:21,132
你最好不是在跟我开玩笑，小女孩！
You better not be toying with me, little girl,

324
00:18:21,134 --> 00:18:24,268
因为我现在情绪很激动受不了半点刺激！
because I am highly emotional and extremely gullible.

325
00:18:24,270 --> 00:18:26,204
我是认真的！
I'm telling the truth.

326
00:18:26,206 --> 00:18:27,939
所以如果你们知道阿拉卡扎的家在那里，
So if one of you knows where Alacazar's house is,

327
00:18:27,941 --> 00:18:29,707
就请带我去吧。
maybe you could take me there.

328
00:18:29,709 --> 00:18:33,778
哇哦，你以为我们是什么，飞马吗？
Whoa ho now, what do we look like, flying horses?

329
00:18:33,780 --> 00:18:35,613
你看到这背上有马鞍了吗？
Do you see a saddle on this back?

330
00:18:35,615 --> 00:18:37,281
淡定，你们两个。
Relax, you two.

331
00:18:37,283 --> 00:18:39,450
- 你叫什么名字？ - 苏菲亚。
- What's your name? - Sofia.

332
00:18:39,452 --> 00:18:42,320
好吧苏菲亚，如果你真的能救回艾莲娜，
Well, Sofia, if you can bring back Elena,

333
00:18:42,322 --> 00:18:44,722
我会带你去阿拉卡扎的家的，
I'll take you to Alacazar's house,

334
00:18:44,724 --> 00:18:46,457
只要有人告诉我他在哪里。。
as soon as someone tells me where it is.

335
00:18:46,459 --> 00:18:48,493
他家就在月亮下的悬崖底下。
It's right below the moon cliff.

336
00:18:48,495 --> 00:18:50,094
有一位老前辈带我去过。
One of the old timers showed me once.

337
00:18:50,096 --> 00:18:51,729
上来吧，公主殿下。
Hop on, Your Highness.

338
00:18:56,903 --> 00:18:58,503
谢谢！
Thanks.

339
00:18:58,505 --> 00:19:01,506
这可能需要习惯一下。
This is gonna take some getting used to.

340
00:19:01,508 --> 00:19:03,341
抓稳了！
Hold on!

341
00:19:14,187 --> 00:19:16,754
你们的国家可真美！
Your kingdom is beautiful.

342
00:19:16,756 --> 00:19:19,423
在史瑞奇统治这里之前比现在还要好！
It looked even better before Shuriki took over.

343
00:19:19,425 --> 00:19:20,525
当然了！
Sure did.

344
00:19:20,527 --> 00:19:22,426
还有声音也很美！
And sounded better, too.

345
00:19:22,428 --> 00:19:23,761
你什么意思？
What do you mean?

346
00:19:23,763 --> 00:19:26,797
- 她规定唱歌会犯法！ - 为什么？
- She outlawed music. - Why?

347
00:19:26,799 --> 00:19:29,367
因为她想要所有人都忘掉从前的阿瓦洛！
Because she wanted everyone to forget the old Avalor.

348
00:19:29,369 --> 00:19:32,003
这就是为什么我们一直坚持唱歌。
That's why we jaquins still sing.

349
00:19:32,005 --> 00:19:36,974
提醒大家阿瓦洛的精神仍然存在。
To remind everyone that the spirit of Avalor lives on.

350
00:19:36,976 --> 00:19:39,043
这也是为什么史瑞奇会那么抓狂！
And 'cause it really bugs Shuriki.

351
00:19:39,045 --> 00:19:42,313
在过去的日子里
? Way back in the old days ?

352
00:19:42,315 --> 00:19:46,384
