00:38:57,202 --> 00:38:59,703
签好了，现在拿去给...
Done. Now that that's taken care of...

714
00:38:59,705 --> 00:39:01,137
史瑞奇！
Shuriki!

715
00:39:01,139 --> 00:39:02,572
- 嗯？ - 嗯？
- Huh? - Huh?

716
00:39:05,811 --> 00:39:07,110
艾莲娜公主！
Princess Elena!

717
00:39:07,112 --> 00:39:09,679
是时候让你为你的所做所为付出代价了！
The time has come to pay for your crimes.

718
00:39:09,681 --> 00:39:11,648
代价？什么代价？
Crimes? What crimes?

719
00:39:11,650 --> 00:39:13,283
史瑞奇入侵了阿瓦洛，
Shuriki invaded Avalor,

720
00:39:13,285 --> 00:39:15,385
并且推翻了皇室的统治！
and overthrew the royal family.

721
00:39:15,387 --> 00:39:16,453
我父亲的统治！
My family.

722
00:39:16,455 --> 00:39:17,554
这是真的吗？
Is this true?

723
00:39:17,556 --> 00:39:19,956
噢，艾莲娜，
Oh, Elena.

724
00:39:19,958 --> 00:39:21,858
一些人有资格继承王位，
Some inherit their kingdoms.

725
00:39:21,860 --> 00:39:25,395
但另一些人得靠强大的力强！
Others have to take theirs by force.

726
00:39:25,397 --> 00:39:26,696
嘿！
Hey!

727
00:39:26,698 --> 00:39:28,798
所以我要靠这个来夺回我的一切！
Then I'm here to take mine back.

728
00:39:28,800 --> 00:39:32,569
但阿瓦洛没有你更加繁荣昌盛，
But Avalor has been so much better without you.

729
00:39:32,571 --> 00:39:34,637
为什么一定要搅和这么好的事情呢？
Why ruin a good thing?

730
00:39:37,576 --> 00:39:39,309
在找这个吗？
Looking for this?

731
00:39:39,311 --> 00:39:41,010
怎么会在你那里？
How did you get that?

732
00:39:41,012 --> 00:39:42,545
肯定是那个小公主，
It was that little princess.

733
00:39:42,547 --> 00:39:43,880
戴项链的那个！
The one with the necklace.

734
00:39:43,882 --> 00:39:46,316
等等，苏菲亚参与了这件事？
Wait. Sofia's involved in this?

735
00:39:46,318 --> 00:39:49,486
没错，就是她把我从护身符里放出来的，
Yes. She freed me from her amulet,

736
00:39:49,488 --> 00:39:51,588
所以我才有机会夺回阿瓦洛！
so that I could free Avalor from you.

737
00:39:51,590 --> 00:39:53,256
噢，我居然被她耍了！
Oh, I don't know about that.

738
00:39:53,258 --> 00:39:56,259
但你不是女巫根本控制不了这么强大的魔法棒。
It takes more than a wand to make you a sorceress.

739
00:39:56,261 --> 00:40:00,063
你的咒语在我的脑海里回荡了40多年，史瑞奇！
Your spell has echoed in my mind for 40 years, Shuriki.

740
00:40:00,065 --> 00:40:01,865
我知道该怎么用！
I know it by heart.

741
00:40:01,867 --> 00:40:03,733
<i>Vadisima!（咒语）</i>

742
00:40:03,735 --> 00:40:05,935


743
00:40:06,938 --> 00:40:09,205
看来你要更努力才行喽！
You'll have to do better than that.

744
00:40:09,207 --> 00:40:10,774
<i>Vadisima!（咒语）</i>

745
00:40:15,781 --> 00:40:17,680


746
00:40:19,418 --> 00:40:22,252
这是什么？
What is this?

747
00:40:22,254 --> 00:40:24,788
我以前从没见过这幅画。
I've never seen this painting before.

748
00:40:24,790 --> 00:40:27,791
哦，这不是普通的画，艾莲娜。
Oh, that's no ordinary painting, Elena.

749
00:40:27,793 --> 00:40:31,428
阿拉卡扎为了保护你妹妹和你祖父母
That's how Alacazar protected your little sister and grandparents--

750
00:40:31,430 --> 00:40:36,199
将他们封印在这幅画里，连我都无法破解！
inside an enchanted painting even my magic cannot touch.

751
00:40:36,201 --> 00:40:39,602
爷爷！奶奶！
Abuelo. Abuela.

752
00:40:39,604 --> 00:40:41,371
伊莎贝尔！
Isabel.

753
00:40:41,373 --> 00:40:43,440
说到家人，
And speaking of family,

754
00:40:43,442 --> 00:40:47,043
你还没向你表哥埃斯特班打招呼呢！
you haven't said hello to your cousin Esteban.

755
00:40:47,045 --> 00:40:48,711


756
00:40:48,713 --> 00:40:50,280
不！
No.

757
00:40:50,282 --> 00:40:52,215
他不可能是埃斯特班！
This cannot be Esteban.

758
00:40:52,217 --> 00:40:55,285
你被困在护身符里太久了，
You were stuck in that amulet a long time.

759
00:40:55,287 --> 00:40:59,055
你或许还是16岁，但埃斯特班已经老了！
You may still be 16, but Esteban grew up.

760
00:40:59,057 --> 00:41:00,757
等等，你在帮她做事？
Wait. You're with her?

761
00:41:00,759 --> 00:41:03,460
我...我别无选择，艾莲娜！
I... I had no choice, Elena.

762
00:41:03,462 --> 00:41:06,563
是这样吗？埃斯特班？
Is that so, Esteban?

763
00:41:06,565 --> 00:41:08,698
<i>Vadisima!（咒语）</i>

764
00:41:10,635 --> 00:41:11,734
抓住她！
Seize her!

765
00:41:16,741 --> 00:41:18,241


766
00:41:18,243 --> 00:41:20,510
找到你们啦！
Found ya!

767
00:41:20,512 --> 00:41:21,678
哦！
Oh!

768
00:41:22,948 --> 00:41:24,848
哈？发生什么了？
Uh, what's going on?

769
00:41:24,850 --> 00:41:26,683
没什么，阿芒多。
Nothing, Armando.

770
00:41:26,685 --> 00:41:28,852
我只是在让这一切变得有条理！
I'm just setting things back in order.

771
00:41:28,854 --> 00:41:31,020
嘿，你太慢了，史瑞奇！
Hey, not so fast, Shuriki!

772
00:41:31,022 --> 00:41:32,021


773
00:41:32,023 --> 00:41:34,324
跳上来，艾莲娜！
Hop on, Elena.

774
00:41:34,326 --> 00:41:36,426
不，等一下，不要走，斯凯勒。
No, wait. Don't leave, Skylar.

775
00:41:36,428 --> 00:41:39,462
<i>Vadisima!（咒语）</i>
卫兵，拦住他们！
Guards, stop them!

776
00:41:39,464 --> 00:41:41,498
给我在黄昏之前抓住她！
I want her captured by nightfall.

777
00:41:41,500 --> 00:41:42,932
还有那个小公主！
Her and that little princess.

778
00:41:42,934 --> 00:41:44,701
这不关苏菲亚的事！
Leave Sofia out of this.

779
00:41:44,703 --> 00:41:47,203
先把他们关起来。
And lock them up while you're at it.

780
00:41:47,205 --> 00:41:48,938
把你的手拿开！
Get your hands off me!

781
00:41:48,940 --> 00:41:50,440
你会后悔的！
You'll regret this.

782
00:41:50,442 --> 00:41:51,674
我才不信你的鬼话！
I doubt it.

783
00:41:51,676 --> 00:41:54,444
停下，停下！
Wait. Wait.

784
00:41:54,446 --> 00:41:56,212
斯凯勒，我们得回去！
Skylar, we have to go back.

785
00:41:56,214 --> 00:41:58,214
为什么？好让她干掉你吗？
Why? So she can finish you off?

786
00:41:58,216 --> 00:41:59,849
你很勇敢，公主，
You are brave, princess,

787
00:41:59,851 --> 00:42:02,785
但你的计划实在是太烂了！
but your battle strategy, not so good.

788
00:42:02,787 --> 00:42:04,854
艾莲娜，这是怎么了？
Elena, what happened?

789
00:42:04,856 --> 00:42:06,890
我尽力了，苏菲亚，
I tried my best, Sofia,

790
00:42:06,892 --> 00:42:08,391
但我并不知道会导致这样的，
but I couldn't get the spell right,

791
00:42:08,393 --> 00:42:09,959
史瑞奇抓住了你的家人！
and Shuriki has your family now.

792
00:42:09,961 --> 00:42:11,694
她抓住了我的家人？
She has my family?

793
00:42:11,696 --> 00:42:13,496
我真的很抱歉！
I'm so sorry.

794
00:42:13,498 --> 00:42:15,832
她在那里，弓箭手，瞄准目标，
There she is. Archers, lock your arrows.

795
00:42:15,834 --> 00:42:17,734
放箭！
Draw!

796
00:42:17,736 --> 00:42:19,836
哇哦，他们在向我们射箭！
Whoa. They're shooting arrows!

797
00:42:19,838 --> 00:42:21,971
快躲开，不要飞直线！
Evasive action. Dodge and weave.

798
00:42:21,973 --> 00:42:23,540
好的！我们那样
Yeah, we could do that.

799
00:42:23,542 --> 00:42:25,141
也许有机会逃出去。
Or we could just get on up outta here.

800
00:42:25,143 --> 00:42:28,043
- 我们可以去我家里。 - 太好了，抓稳了！
- We can go to my place. - Great. Hang on.

801
00:42:44,763 --> 00:42:46,462
噢，真希望他们没事！
Oh, I hope they're okay.

802
00:42:52,270 --> 00:42:55,271
怎么会发生这种事？罗伦，苏菲亚到底去哪儿了？
This is not okay, Roland. Where is Sofia?

803
00:42:55,273 --> 00:42:58,741
我会有办法出去的，美兰达，我们也会找到苏菲亚的！
I will get us out of here, Miranda, and we will find Sofia.

804
00:42:58,743 --> 00:43:02,345
囚犯们已经被关起来了，埃斯特班大臣。
The prisoners are secured, Chancellor Esteban.

805
00:43:02,347 --> 00:43:04,614
那些囚犯可是皇室成员，
Those prisoners are royalty,

806
00:43:04,616 --> 00:43:06,215
你就这样对待他们？
and you will treat them as such.

807
00:43:06,217 --> 00:43:08,017
是的，埃斯特班大臣。
Yes, chancellor.

808
00:43:08,019 --> 00:43:11,621
哎呀呀！真是一波未平一波又起呀！
Ay yi yi. Yet another mess to clean up.

809
00:43:11,623 --> 00:43:13,890
这么说艾莲娜公主还活着？
So Princess Elena lives.

810
00:43:13,892 --> 00:43:16,025
很显然。
Apparently so.

811
00:43:16,027 --> 00:43:17,694
她是王位的合法继承人。
She is the rightful heir to the throne.

812
00:43:17,696 --> 00:43:19,128
我们应该帮帮她！
We should be helping her.

813
00:43:19,130 --> 00:43:21,197
你想要我们怎么做，嗯？
What do you suggest we do, hmm?

814
00:43:21,199 --> 00:43:23,866
向女王发起挑战？可我们还是会输。
Fight the queen? Because we will lose.

815
00:43:23,868 --> 00:43:25,868
但艾莲娜是的表妹啊，埃斯特班！
But Elena's your cousin, Esteban.

816
00:43:25,870 --> 00:43:28,805
她的祖父母视我如己出，
And her grandparents raised me like a son.

817
00:43:28,807 --> 00:43:31,207
我每天都在回想当时发生的一切，
And I think about what happened to them every day.

818
00:43:31,209 --> 00:43:34,844
所以不用你提醒我该怎么做，阿芒多。
So I do not need you to remind me, Armando.

819
00:43:55,133 --> 00:43:58,901
艾莲娜，那里发生了什么？
Elena, what happened back there?

820
00:44:02,273 --> 00:44:04,474
直到今天我才知道
I never knew what happened

821
00:44:04,476 --> 00:44:07,577
在我妹妹和祖父母身上发生了什么。
to my sister and my grandparents until today.

822
00:44:07,579 --> 00:44:10,079
看到他们被困在那幅画里，
Seeing them trapped in that painting

823
00:44:10,081 --> 00:44:12,682
让我想起我最后一次见到伊莎贝尔的时候。
reminded me of the last time I saw Isabel.

824
00:44:12,684 --> 00:44:15,151
- 伊莎贝尔？ - 我妹妹。
- Isabel? - My little sister.

825
00:44:15,153 --> 00:44:17,854
她整天都呆在花园里，
She'd been out in the garden all day,

826
00:44:17,856 --> 00:44:19,822
给那些飞豹造喂料机。
building a new feeder for the jaquins.

827
00:44:19,824 --> 00:44:21,858
还把自己弄得一身脏，
She was filthy,

828
00:44:21,860 --> 00:44:23,993
爸爸妈妈要赶回家吃晚饭
and our parents were on their way home for dinner,

829
00:44:23,995 --> 00:44:25,828
所以我叫她去换身衣服，
so I asked her to change.

830
00:44:25,830 --> 00:44:27,930
她就换了干净的裙子回来了，
And she comes back wearing a clean dress,

831
00:44:27,932 --> 00:44:32,135
但手上和脸上还是一团糟，
but her hands and face are still covered in dirt.

832
00:44:32,137 --> 00:44:35,004
我刚帮她擦干净
I had just finished cleaning her off

833
00:44:35,006 --> 00:44:39,275
就听到了外面有马车的声音
when I heard our parents' carriage pull up outside.

834
00:44:39,277 --> 00:44:41,678
然后，史瑞奇来了。
And then, Shuriki arrived.

835
00:44:41,680 --> 00:44:43,546
我很抱歉。
I'm sorry.

836
00:44:43,548 --> 00:44:46,649
当我看到她被封印在画里的时候，
When I saw her in that enchanted painting today,

837
00:44:46,651 --> 00:44:48,885
发现她的脸上还有一团泥巴，
she still had a smudge on her cheek.

838
00:44:48,887 --> 00:44:50,787
我猜肯定是我忽略了。
I guess I missed a spot.

839
00:44:50,789 --> 00:44:53,222


840
00:44:53,224 --> 00:44:56,659
我们有能救出他们的咒语。
We have the spell that can get them out.

841
00:44:56,661 --> 00:44:58,027
- 我们有吗？ - 当然有！
- We do? - We do.

842
00:44:58,029 --> 00:45:00,396
你爷爷在他离开之前告诉过我，
Your grandfather showed me where it was

843
00:45:00,398 --> 00:45:03,366
但我从没学过魔法，
before he left, but I never learned magic,

844
00:45:03,368 --> 00:45:05,168
所以我没法解除咒语。
so I cannot cast the spell.

845
00:45:05,170 --> 00:45:07,070
但你可以，马泰奥。
You will have to do it, Mateo.

846
00:45:07,072 --> 00:45:09,872
啊，你为什么认为我可以呢？
And, uh, why would I be able to do it?

847
00:45:09,874 --> 00:45:12,375
马泰奥，你以前在地下室里
Mateo, you're down there in the basement

848
00:45:12,377 --> 00:45:14,544
没日没夜的练习魔法，
practicing magic day and night.

849
00:45:14,546 --> 00:45:15,912
你以为我不知道吗？
You think I don't know this?

850
00:45:15,914 --> 00:45:18,147
但是艾莲娜，我必需提醒你，
But Elena, I must warn you.

851
00:45:18,149 --> 00:45:21,350
在打败史瑞奇之前最好不要救他们出来，
To bring them out with Shuriki still in power

852
00:45:21,352 --> 00:45:23,352
那会让他们陷入危险之中。
will put them in great danger.

853
00:45:23,354 --> 00:45:25,988


854
00:45:25,990 --> 00:45:29,025
有人来了，快藏起来，马上！
We have visitors. Quick, hide, over there.

855
00:45:29,027 --> 00:45:32,628
好的，来啦，来啦！
Okay. Coming, coming.

856
00:45:35,834 --> 00:45:37,934
拉法，你听说了吗？
Rafa, did you hear?

857
00:45:37,936 --> 00:45:40,536
他们说艾莲娜公主回来了。
They're saying that Princess Elena has returned.

858
00:45:40,538 --> 00:45:43,539
哦，快，快进来！
Oh, hurry. Hurry. Come inside.

859
00:45:43,541 --> 00:45:45,575
我们得小心点！
We have to be careful.

860
00:45:45,577 --> 00:45:47,510
艾莲娜公主，没事的，
Princess Elena, it's okay.

861
00:45:47,512 --> 00:45:49,412
我们可以信任他们！
We can trust them.

862
00:45:53,017 --> 00:45:54,183
这是真的！
It is true.

863
00:45:54,185 --> 00:45:56,052
公主还活着！
The princess lives!

864
00:45:56,054 --> 00:45:57,120
我的公主。
My princess.

865
00:45:57,122 --> 00:45:59,088
你们不用向我行礼。
You don't have to bow.

866
00:45:59,090 --> 00:46:00,590
哦，好吧！
Oh, okay.

867
00:46:00,592 --> 00:46:02,125
我们随时听候您的差遣。
We are at your command.

868
00:46:02,127 --> 00:46:04,794
跟史瑞奇抗争到底！
I will take on Shuriki myself.

869
00:46:04,796 --> 00:46:06,696
谢谢你，你们大家，
Thank you, all of you,

870
00:46:06,698 --> 00:46:09,065
但这是我的战斗，不是你们的。
but this is my fight, not yours.

871
00:46:09,067 --> 00:46:11,801
我必须独自面对她。
I'm the one who must face her.

872
00:46:11,803 --> 00:46:15,805
只有你能做到的事并不代表你要一个人去做。
You may be the one, but you're not the only one.

873
00:46:15,807 --> 00:46:18,641
祖佐告诉我的，我想我知道这是什么意思了！
Zuzo said that, and now I know what he meant.

874
00:46:18,643 --> 00:46:20,443
那好吧，那是什么意思？
Okay. What did he mean?

875
00:46:20,445 --> 00:46:22,945
我们都可以帮到你，你不用独自面对史瑞奇。
We can all help. You don't need to face Shuriki alone.

876
00:46:22,947 --> 00:46:25,248
你只要告诉我们该怎么做。
You just need to tell us what to do.

877
00:46:25,250 --> 00:46:28,084
你知道吗？我从护身符里
You know, all this time

878
00:46:28,086 --> 00:46:30,787
出来的时候，我一直以为我是一个人，
I was stuck in the amulet, I thought I was alone,

879
00:46:30,789 --> 00:46:33,156
但你说得对，苏菲亚，我不应该这样想，
but you're right, Sofia. It doesn't have to be that way.

880
00:46:33,158 --> 00:46:34,991
我还有你们。
I have all of you.

881
00:46:34,993 --> 00:46:39,061
是啊，但我们要怎么对付史瑞奇和那些士兵呢？
Yeah, but what good are we against Shuriki and all her soldiers?

882
00:46:39,063 --> 00:46:41,564
我还在想，
I'm still figuring that out,

883
00:46:41,566 --> 00:46:43,766
但我需要所有人的帮助！
but I'm going to need everyone's help.

884
00:46:43,768 --> 00:46:45,601
- 我们与你同在。 - 一直都是！
- We're with you. - All the way.

885
00:46:45,603 --> 00:46:46,969
不只是你们，
Not just you.

886
00:46:46,971 --> 00:46:48,704
我是说所有人！
Everyone.

887
00:47:15,033 --> 00:47:16,833
我们在哪儿？
Where are we?

888
00:47:16,835 --> 00:47:19,135
这是通往皇宫的一条秘道。
A secret back entrance to the palace.

889
00:47:19,137 --> 00:47:22,605
我以为我永远都不会走这条路。
Not that I ever snuck out when I wasn't supposed to.

890
00:47:32,350 --> 00:47:34,317
我在会合的地方找你，斯凯勒。
I'll see you at the rendezvous point, Skylar.

891
00:47:34,319 --> 00:47:36,953
你最好！
You better.

892
00:47:36,955 --> 00:47:39,322
我们要怎么找到我的家人？
How will we find my family?

893
00:47:39,324 --> 00:47:41,724
史瑞奇只会把他们关在一个地方。
There's only one place Shuriki would've put them.

894
00:47:45,396 --> 00:47:46,629
艾莲娜公主？！
Princess Elena?!

895
00:47:46,631 --> 00:47:50,633
你好，你看上去是个好人，
Hey there. You look like a nice guy

896
00:47:50,635 --> 00:47:52,535
谁想做正确的事？
who just wants to do the right thing.

897
00:47:52,537 --> 00:47:55,037
我吗？我是说，我想！
I do? I mean, I do.

898
00:47:55,039 --> 00:47:56,706
无论什么事情，公主。
Whatever you need, princess.

899
00:47:56,708 --> 00:47:58,074
我都会听候你的差遣！
I am at your service.

900
00:48:02,680 --> 00:48:04,213
啊嗯，打扰一下，
Ahem. Excuse me,

901
00:48:04,215 --> 00:48:06,716
史瑞奇女王想让你们两个去
but Queen Shuriki wants the both of you

902
00:48:06,718 --> 00:48:08,351
给她报告情况。
to report to her right away.

903
00:48:08,353 --> 00:48:11,254
我去，你守在这里。
I'll go. You stay here.

904
00:48:11,256 --> 00:48:13,923
不行，她说让你们两个都去！
No, but she asked to see the both of you.

905
00:48:13,925 --> 00:48:15,725
我们中必须有个人守着囚犯。
One of us has to watch the prisoners.

906
00:48:15,727 --> 00:48:17,994
嗯，等一下，别关门！
Um, wait. Hold on.

907
00:48:19,764 --> 00:48:21,597
好痛！
That hurts.

908
00:48:21,599 --> 00:48:24,267
