There's only one way to find out.

914
00:48:34,412 --> 00:48:36,779
我希望我能变小。
I wish I was small.

915
00:48:38,383 --> 00:48:40,082


916
00:48:40,084 --> 00:48:43,286
阿芒多，我需要你去分散警卫的注意力。
Armando, I need you to distract the guard.

917
00:48:45,089 --> 00:48:48,457
你好，打扰一下，你好！
Hello. Excuse me. Hello.

918
00:48:48,459 --> 00:48:50,293
又怎么了？
What is it now?

919
00:48:50,295 --> 00:48:52,895
有一件非常非常重要的事情，
There's something very, very important

920
00:48:52,897 --> 00:48:54,597
我必须告诉你，就在这里。
I must tell you. Over here.

921
00:48:58,102 --> 00:49:00,002
我想要变回来。
I wish to be big again.

922
00:49:06,277 --> 00:49:08,411
- 嗨！ - 苏菲亚！
- Hi. - Sofia!

923
00:49:08,413 --> 00:49:09,645
嘘！我们得赶紧。
Sh. We have to hurry.

924
00:49:09,647 --> 00:49:11,080
你要解释的事情够多了！
You have a lot of explaining to do.

925
00:49:11,082 --> 00:49:13,816
妈妈，我...会解释的，我保证！
Mom, I will... later. I promise.

926
00:49:13,818 --> 00:49:16,819
但现在我们得想个办法对付警卫！
But right now, we have to find a way to get past that guard.

927
00:49:16,821 --> 00:49:19,088
我来对付他。
I'll take care of him.

928
00:49:19,090 --> 00:49:21,557
当农夫跟着她进入丛林，
And when the farmer followed her into the jungle,

929
00:49:21,559 --> 00:49:24,961
她突然变成了一只凶猛的豹子！
she turned into a jaguar!

930
00:49:24,963 --> 00:49:27,296
