This is the important thing you had to tell me?

931
00:49:27,298 --> 00:49:29,265
你得听我讲完！
You haven't heard the ending yet.

932
00:49:29,267 --> 00:49:31,133
抓住他！
Grab him!

933
00:49:33,237 --> 00:49:34,837
抓住他了！
Got him!

934
00:49:34,839 --> 00:49:36,339
干得好！
Well done.

935
00:49:41,245 --> 00:49:43,579
爸爸，这位是艾莲娜公主。
Dad, this is Princess Elena.

936
00:49:43,581 --> 00:49:46,315
我很抱歉给你的家人带来危险，
I'm sorry for the danger I put your family in.

937
00:49:46,317 --> 00:49:48,184
但我等一位公主把我从
But I've waited so many years

938
00:49:48,186 --> 00:49:51,087
