So when I was picking out Sofia's welcome gift,

942
00:49:59,030 --> 00:50:01,030
是你让护身符发光的对吗？
it was you who made the amulet glow?

943
00:50:01,032 --> 00:50:03,265
没错，我需要一个足够年轻的小孩子
Yes. I needed someone young enough

944
00:50:03,267 --> 00:50:06,268
