Sofia, you still should've told us what was going on.

949
00:50:14,545 --> 00:50:17,446
我知道，但我不想给你们添麻烦。
I know. I just wanted to keep you all out of trouble.

950
00:50:17,448 --> 00:50:19,215
好吧，但我们知道得也太晚了吧！
Well, it's too late for that.

951
00:50:19,217 --> 00:50:22,051
我想这次就原谅你吧！
I think a pardon may be in order just this once.

952
00:50:22,053 --> 00:50:24,353
我有一个能保证你们安全的计划，
I have a plan to get you all to safety,

953
00:50:24,355 --> 00:50:26,122
但我们得赶紧。
but we have to hurry.

954
00:50:26,124 --> 00:50:28,557
我已经没有耐心了，埃斯特班。
I'm losing my patience, Esteban.

955
00:50:28,559 --> 00:50:30,359
艾莲娜公主到底在哪里？
Where is Princess Elena?

956
00:50:30,361 --> 00:50:33,229
史瑞奇，当我帮你入侵阿瓦洛的时候，
Queen Shuriki, when I helped you invade Avalor,

957
00:50:33,231 --> 00:50:36,665
