you promised me that no one in my family would be hurt.

958
00:50:36,667 --> 00:50:40,169
我也答应给你权力，看看你现在，
I also promised you power, and look at you now,

959
00:50:40,171 --> 00:50:42,371
埃斯特班大臣。
Chancellor Esteban.

960
00:50:42,373 --> 00:50:45,875
