Just be happy I kept one of my promises,

961
00:50:45,877 --> 00:50:48,744
否则你会像你阿姨和叔叔一样。
or you'll wind up like your aunt and uncle.

962
00:50:48,746 --> 00:50:50,546
你要见我吗？女王陛下。
You wanted to see me, Your Grace.

963
00:50:50,548 --> 00:50:54,417
在找到那两个公主之前我不想见任何人！
I don't want to see anyone until those princesses are found.

964
00:50:54,419 --> 00:50:56,419
你好哇，史瑞奇。
Hey there, Shuriki.

965
00:50:56,421 --> 00:50:58,354
好久不见。
Long time no see.

966
00:50:58,356 --> 00:51:02,391
在外面我还能忍你，但在我的宫殿里不可能！
I've put up with you buzzards outside, but not in my palace.

967
00:51:02,393 --> 00:51:04,427
但这里很舒服，
But it's so comfy in here.

968
00:51:04,429 --> 00:51:06,495
哦，这个栖息地可真不错！
Ooh, here's a nice little perch.

969
00:51:06,497 --> 00:51:07,897
从我的王座上下来。
Get off my throne.

970
00:51:07,899 --> 00:51:09,899
- <i>Vadisima!（咒语）</i>
- 没打中！
- Missed me!

971
00:51:09,901 --> 00:51:11,600
抓住那头野兽！
Capture that beast.

972
00:51:11,602 --> 00:51:13,836
你听说女王说的了吗？快去！
You heard the queen. Move!

973
00:51:13,838 --> 00:51:15,304
遵命！
Yes, sir.

974
00:51:20,878 --> 00:51:23,079
好的，我来看下咒语。
Okay, let's see the spell.

975
00:51:23,081 --> 00:51:26,615
哇哦！
Whoa.
<i>Tlah...cui...lolli...?</i>

976
00:51:26,617 --> 00:51:28,551
哦，伙计，这简直就是绕口令！
Oh, boy, that's a tongue twister.

977
00:51:28,553 --> 00:51:29,718
马泰奥！
Mateo!

978
00:51:29,720 --> 00:51:31,987
噢，是你们啊！
Oh, it's you.

979
00:51:33,591 --> 00:51:35,424
哦，伊莎贝尔！
Oh, Isabel!

980
00:51:35,426 --> 00:51:37,026
你得救他们出来，马泰奥。
You have to get them out, Mateo.

981
00:51:37,028 --> 00:51:38,594
现在。
Now.

982
00:51:38,596 --> 00:51:39,895
好的。
Okay.

983
00:51:39,897 --> 00:51:42,465
<i>Tlahcuilolli apartad.（咒语）</i>

984
00:51:42,467 --> 00:51:44,366
<i>Tlahcuilolli apareced.（咒语）</i>

985
00:51:44,368 --> 00:51:46,702
<i> Tlahcuilolli vivid!（咒语）</i>

986
00:51:55,146 --> 00:51:57,947
- 伊莎贝尔！ - 艾莲娜！
- Isabel! - Elena!

987
00:51:57,949 --> 00:52:00,282
我好想你。
I missed you so much.

988
00:52:00,284 --> 00:52:02,151
让我...
Let me just...

989
00:52:02,153 --> 00:52:04,120
你安全了。
You're safe.

990
00:52:04,122 --> 00:52:06,555
爷爷，奶奶！
Abuelo,abuela.

991
00:52:07,992 --> 00:52:10,926
宫殿看起来有点不一样啊！
The palace looks so different.

992
00:52:10,928 --> 00:52:13,796
- 史瑞奇呢？ - 她还在这里。
- What happened to Shuriki? - She's still here.

993
00:52:13,798 --> 00:52:17,433
我就不应该让阿拉克扎把我们封在画里。
I never should've let Alacazar put us in that painting.

994
00:52:17,435 --> 00:52:18,901
呃，我们可以等一下再说这件事吗？
Uh, can we talk about this later?

995
00:52:18,903 --> 00:52:20,736
我们得走了！
We have to go.

996
00:52:23,307 --> 00:52:25,741
大家抓紧时间，骑上飞豹。
