997
00:52:25,743 --> 00:52:27,343
哇哦，公主。
Whoa, princess.

998
00:52:27,345 --> 00:52:29,311
你应该告诉我一个准确数，
You should've given me a head count.

999
00:52:29,313 --> 00:52:31,147
