should return to the ship where it's safe.

1011
00:53:09,887 --> 00:53:11,353
我们不会有事的，爸爸！
We'll be okay, Dad.

1012
00:53:11,355 --> 00:53:13,189
我们不是孤军奋战，所有人都会帮我们！
We won't be alone. Everyone's coming.

