00:54:01,172 --> 00:54:03,005
什么？
What?

1032
00:54:03,007 --> 00:54:04,907
那是什么声音？
What is that sound?

1033
00:54:06,577 --> 00:54:08,377
他们来了，女王陛下！
They're coming, Your Majesty.

1034
00:54:08,379 --> 00:54:09,445
谁来了？
Who is coming?

1035
00:54:09,447 --> 00:54:10,679
