That'll work, too.

1060
00:56:09,800 --> 00:56:11,367
团结一致，
Stay together.

1061
00:56:11,369 --> 00:56:13,635
齐心协力！
Stay strong!

1062
00:56:13,637 --> 00:56:15,504
镇定，土兵！
Stand firm, men.

1063
00:56:15,506 --> 00:56:17,973
